  PreLevelDialogue:
  - KID, SLAP ME.
  - Am I dreaming?
  - " We got an offer we physically can\u2019t refuse. It\u2019s a bit crazy, BUT
    this will put us on the map!"
  - "Right now we\u2019re just dawgs, we do this well, WE ENLARGE KID, we become
    big dawgs!"
  - "Okay I\u2019ll slow down, have you heard of Tim Apple? He wants OUR sculptures."
  - Mhm, OURS! He is paying us BIG for this.
  - "I am warning you though, these sculptures are HARD, you\u2019re going to have
    to use all of the skills you\u2019ve gained over the past couple orders to smash
    this out of the park."
  - "Get this done well, and ol\u2019 Bill will get the first THREE rounds, I\u2019ll
    even get you that expensive sake you like."
  - "Alright DON\u2019T let Bill down!"
